Class MLModel.ClassAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • ml.MLModel.ClassAttribute
  • Enclosing class:
    MLModel

    protected static class MLModel.ClassAttribute
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores the possible values for attributes of type Class and a numeric representation. The latter can be used for training and prediction.
